      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey can u help me out? im planning a weekend trip and trying to pick where to stay. whats the difference in the 'vibe' between a place like Upper West Side in NYC and somewhere like East Oakland? like, which one would be more welcoming or easier for a tourist to just wander around in?",
